{
  "texts": [
    "Distributed databases like Blockchain can play a significant role in maintaining patients' medical data with safety and security.",
    "It is also considered a trusted platform because all nodes that execute in this Blockchain network are verified All nodes in the Blockchain network should be supplied by healthcare providers, individuals, or other organizations.",
    "Nodes are labeled with some categories in this private Blockchain network.",
    "The categorical label of the nodes can be expressed as general, benign, half, and miner nodes which is a kind of Bitcoin Blockchain.",
    "Here, healthcare professionals, healthcare providers, or individual users are labeled as half nodes and are interested in conducting patient's medical data that is saved in the Blockchain network."
  ]
}